The UV-vis spectra of TiO2 and ZnFeAl-LDHs/TiO2(b) are shown in Fig. 4(b). It can be seen that pure TiO2 exhibits a steep absorption edge at approximately 380 nm. In addition, a red shift of the absorption edge is observed in ZnFeAl-LDHs/TiO2(b), inducing stronger light absorption in the visible region. And the band gap of the two samples were achieved followed the equation,1(Ahν)2=K(hν−Eg)n/2\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
